--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.3.0 (2021-01-07)
F: Update Prometheus to version 2.24.0

* Version 0.2.1 (2020-12-13)
F: Add alerting rules for chrony_check-time and openntpd_check-time

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-12-13)
C: Remove dnf_check-update and yum_check-update script status

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-12-12)
F: Initial release
